detaileddescription.para: A rule consists of a symbol, filter expression and range of scales. If filter is empty, it matches all features. If scale range has both values zero, it matches all scales. If one of the min/max scale denominators is zero, there is no lower/upper bound for scales. A rule matches if both filter and scale range match.
